{"tid":2242880,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"各位銀行業嘅靚仔靚女請入","createTime":"2020-10-14T10:38:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T10:56:48.000Z","uid":120746,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"92ab57d3358ffada55c6bede49fcba42b1e6f44c","tid":2242880,"uid":120746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T10:38:39.000Z","msg":"話說最近某某銀行俾左個offer我<br />\n但人工入面包埋rental reimbursement<br />\n咁細佬我就有個doubt<br />\n請問如果我冇租屋住 咁呢筆rental reimbursement<br />\n會否照係人工俾我？<br />\n例如佢份約寫12萬一年 包埋rental reimbursement<br />\n咁如果我冇租屋住 人工係咪一個月一萬"},{"pid":"9a51c6d2be8e5abd54c4d85e3bf36c06b60c2c8a","tid":2242880,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T10:39:46.000Z","msg":"你冇死到人壽會唔會照賠畀你？"},{"pid":"4583e7cca8c6ae085445465ae3be1c91b576d055","tid":2242880,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T10:42:11.000Z","msg":"where"},{"pid":"055bed8bc933872110e866f79987c78eaa0ab808","tid":2242880,"uid":23923,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T10:43:18.000Z","msg":"冇人會理你點用啲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d0ad371c9f46b1d4d5fbdb501aae2e57f5b268","tid":2242880,"uid":123499,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T10:43:37.000Z","msg":"如果包埋不如直接寫落你人工到算啦"},{"pid":"3f5eb6f7f09b77e733a1cd76f0ba0a18ca2f5c52","tid":2242880,"uid":180401,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T10:45:50.000Z","msg":"唔係 要提供租樓證明<br />\n自己物業會無津貼<br />\n之前份工有房屋津貼<br />\n<br />\n不過我諗要睇返公司"},{"pid":"994c23e6a84f18fcfc7789119bb5cf3c4a6313ce","tid":2242880,"uid":63549,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T10:47:49.000Z","msg":"你唔好戇居啦<br />\nrental reimbursement 只係喺你個人工到classify 一部分做公司幫你出嘅 &rdquo;租金&ldquo; 報去IRS <br />\n即係你入息少咗，入息稅有可能低啲 （其他收入要加返個 factor)<br />\n稅局通常有要求公司叫你交租單做證據嘅<br />\n自己錢，自己研究下啦"},{"pid":"a83310343a44d3ef552784abcdd88c835fcf2f34","tid":2242880,"uid":20429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T10:53:32.000Z","msg":"因為租金津貼同薪金唔同扣稅quota<br />\n只係濕鳩細行想慳果少少稅所以咁樣出俾你<br />\n你有租屋供樓就自己都慳咗稅，報稅時唔好填錯<br />\n無就無分別<br />\n唔會唔撚出俾你"},{"pid":"84e8866f83fd87d33ddf7ce52e0e56e0fafd60be","tid":2242880,"uid":266718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"994c23e6a84f18fcfc7789119bb5cf3c4a6313ce","tid":2242880,"uid":63549,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T10:47:49.000Z","msg":"你唔好戇居啦<br />\nrental reimbursement 只係喺你個人工到classify 一部分做公司幫你出嘅 &rdquo;租金&ldquo; 報去IRS <br />\n即係你入息少咗，入息稅有可能低啲 （其他收入要加返個 factor)<br />\n稅局通常有要求公司叫你交租單做證據嘅<br />\n自己錢，自己研究下啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T10:56:48.000Z","msg":"正解"}]}